HTML
> All about the tags

html> main tags
head> contains all  script, title, meta, css
(thing website use internally)
body> content which is visible to the customers


//////////////
Inline > start in same line (span , a)
Block > start from new line (p , h1)

SEO > Search Engine optimisation

////css////
> inline css > we write inside the html tag
> style Tag > we write css in head tag
> styleSheet >  we write css in separate file

inline > styletag > stylesheet

inline{
    color:red;
    font-size:30px
}

styletag{
    color:orange;
    text-align:center
}

stylesheet{
    color:green;
    text-align:right;
    font-size:40px;
    font-weight:bold
}

{
  color:red;
  font-size:30px;  
  text-align:center;
  font-weight:bold;
}

